snippet.title: Fortnite - Season 9 - Battle Pass Overview
snippet.description:
A new season also means a brand new Battle Pass. Over 100 new exclusive rewards are ready for you to unlock, and it still costs the same 950 V-bucks. This season, you’ll get the Sentinel Outfit and Rox progressive Outfit instantly when you purchase the Battle Pass

Play Fortnite Battle Royale, the completely free 100-player PvP mode. One giant map, A Battle Bus, Last one standing wins. ESRB Rating: Teen with Violence.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fortnite/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FortniteGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FortniteGame/

Learn More: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/
